These manuals are written in simple HTML. To automatically generate
table of contents, use the `html-update-toc` script available from
Michael Ernst's software site:

http://www.cs.washington.edu/homes/mernst/software/#html-update


Code snippets tend to be highlighted with syntaxhighlighter. If you
want to add new languages or see how to configure highlighters, see
the project website:

http://alexgorbatchev.com/SyntaxHighlighter/